

// Hooks

Scenario hooks -> which runs before and After Hooks
Step Hooks --> runs before and after each Steps
Conditional Hooks --> Hooks associated with tags for conditional execution.



@Before, @After --> runs before and after every scenario
@BeforeStep

@Before(order=1)  -> for before the order works in ascending order
@Before(order=2)


@After(order=2) --> It works in descending order.... number2 will get executed first and number 1 gets executed second
@After(order=1) 


# Conditional Hooks
@Before(value="@smoke", order =1)


#Hooks with tags
@Before("@smoke")  --> mention a particular tags